Package gov.fnal.ppd.dd

Fermilab's Dynamic Displays System -- top-level package.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChannelSelector
    Allows the user to select the Channel that is being displayed on each Display in the Dynamic Displays system
    DDSystemStatus
    A messaging client that shows what is in the messaging system, taylored to the specifics of the Dynamic Displays system
    GlobalVariables
    This is where all the globakl constant in the Dynamic Displays system are held.
    IdentifyAll
    Let the user ask each Display in the Dynamic Display system to go to the "Identify" screen.

Package gov.fnal.ppd.dd Description

Fermilab's Dynamic Displays System -- top-level package. Defines the main GUI classes for the DD system: ChannelSelector and DDSystemStatus.
